      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm super excited to find a new home for this beauty! It\u2019s been such a fantastic companion and is still running like a total champ. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for all your weekend getaways or daily commutes. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I just know you\u2019re going to love how smooth it feels on the road. It's ready to go whenever you are\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
