    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, a purist\u2019s spec featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Crucially for this chassis, the subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced\u2014addressing the primary failure points of the platform. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and an upgraded coilover setup for improved damping characteristics. While the paintwork shows some road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization is superb, offering the visceral feedback and linear power delivery expected of a well-maintained M-car. This is a driver-grade example optimized for performance and longevity.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
