    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous metallic finish that has been regularly clay-barred and waxed; while you might find the occasional minor stone chip consistent with careful road use, the body lines remain straight and free of significant blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary. The premium leather seats have been treated regularly to maintain their suppleness, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every switch, dial, and digital interface functions exactly as intended, and the interior retains a fresh, non-smoker scent. Under the hood, the engine purrs with the confidence of a machine that has never missed an oil change. The transmission shifts are crisp and intuitive, and the suspension remains tight, soaking up road imperfections without any rattles or stray noises. We have kept a meticulous log of all preventative maintenance, ensuring this car is ready for its next chapter without any immediate service needs. It is a reliable, eye-catching daily driver that has been treated with the respect it deserves.",
      "price": 34500.0,
